sudo /home/ubuntu/AppHadoop/hadoop-1.2.1/bin/hadoop jar /home/ubuntu/AppHadoop/giraph-1.2.0-for-hadoop-1.2.1/giraph-examples-1.2.0.jar org.apache.giraph.GiraphRunner 'giraph.lri.rrojas.rankdegree.LPGPartitionner$ConverterPropagate' -w 1 -vif giraph.lri.rrojas.rankdegree.RR_BGRAP_InputFormat -vip ~/bdrp_data/testfile.txt -vof giraph.lri.rrojas.rankdegree.RR_BGRAP_OuputFormat -op ~/bdrp_output/0126_224320_InitializeSampleRD_testfile.txt_1_folder -ca giraph.masterComputeClass='giraph.lri.rrojas.rankdegree.LPGPartitionner$RDEBMasterCompute' -ca giraph.edgeValueClass=giraph.ml.grafos.okapi.spinner.EdgeValue -ca giraph.vertexValueClass=giraph.ml.grafos.okapi.spinner.VertexValue -ca giraph.outEdgesClass=giraph.lri.rrojas.rankdegree.ShortBooleanHashMapsEdgesInOut -ca giraph.inputOutEdgesClass=giraph.lri.rrojas.rankdegree.ShortBooleanHashMapsEdgesInOut -ca giraph.numComputeThreads=1,giraph.numInputThreads=1,giraph.numOutputThreads=1 -ca giraph.SplitMasterWorker=false -ca spinner.numberOfPartitions=4 -ca graph.directed=true -ca bgrap.SAMPLING_TYPE=InitializeSampleRD -ca bgrap.GRAPH='testfile.txt' -ca bgrap.DATE='0126_224320' -ca rankdegree.TAU='5' -ca rankdegree.SIGMA='0.01' -ca rankdegree.BETA='0.1' -ca rankdegree.SAVE_DD='true'
